持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n5. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n6. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n7. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n8. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n9. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"b7c7b74a949a3715618593bfa45246838904bae7","tid":1535500,"uid":174588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:23:58.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0b794cbdb4375530d9fac736991ee70d60cc22","tid":1535500,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:31:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9707cb5b830fd6c848550545c6fa16c6ac61a7a","tid":1535500,"uid":174588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">推到有消息！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">諗下之後 普教中x國歌法x奴隸制評分 真係洗腦效果x10倍！！</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebd319b34a0e72c92f4a4d0a81bab2186fb5ec0","tid":1535500,"uid":174588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:42:26.000Z","msg":"推啊！"},{"pid":"b390df6867379304d18073cffa0b3a1ee733d9db","tid":1535500,"uid":263344,"like"